      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been consistently maintained. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts reliably, making it an excellent choice for a daily driver. Inside, the cabin is clean and well-kept, though there is some light wear on the upholstery and minor scuffs on the dashboard. The exterior paint retains a nice shine, with only a few small stone chips and light surface scratches visible upon close inspection. Buyers can expect a dependable car that is ready for the road with no immediate repairs needed.",
