    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am honestly so sad to see this one go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014it\u2019s been my total pride and joy and has been babied since day one! It looks and drives just like it did the day it left the showroom, with a spotless interior and a shine that really turns heads. If you're looking for something that feels brand new and has been meticulously cared for, you\u2019ve definitely found it. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I\u2019d love to see it go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S, featuring the coveted wide-body chassis and a naturally aspirated 3.6L flat-six engine with VarioCam Plus. This example is mechanically flawless, boasting a documented LN Engineering IMS bearing retrofit and a fresh rear main seal. The 6-speed manual transaxle offers crisp, short-throw engagement, paired with a viscous-clutch AWD system for exceptional lateral grip. The chassis remains taut with factory-spec Bilstein dampers, while the braking system utilizes cross-drilled rotors and four-piston monobloc calipers. Finished in flawless Arctic Silver over a pristine leather interior, this C4S represents the pinnacle of analog driving dynamics.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Mint condition. No scratches. No dents. Clean title. Full service history. Ready for inspection.",
      "price": 42500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is the definition of a time capsule. Finished in its original factory paint with a deep, mirror-like luster, it has been professionally ceramic coated and kept in a climate-controlled garage since day one. There are no chips, scratches, or swirl marks to be found on the bodywork. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear or creasing, and the interior still retains that fresh-from-the-factory scent. Every electronic feature, from the high-resolution infotainment system to the climate control, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It has been meticulously maintained at the dealership with a documented paper trail of every scheduled service and inspection. The engine bay is spotless, and the undercarriage shows no signs of road salt or oxidation. It drives exactly as it did on the showroom floor\u2014tight, responsive, and incredibly smooth. If you are looking for an example that requires zero apologies and zero immediate investment, this is it. Sale includes both original keys, the factory window sticker, and a complete binder of service records.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
